<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>About Us</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    body {
      background-color: #fffaf5;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      color: #333;
    }

    .about-container {
      max-width: 960px;
      margin: 60px auto;
      padding: 40px;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
    }

    h1 {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 2.8rem;
      color: #e74c3c;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .subtitle {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      color: #666;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    .section-title {
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      color: #c0392b;
      margin-top: 30px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }

    ul {
      padding-left: 20px;
      margin-top: 15px;
    }

    ul li {
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
    }

    .closing {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 40px;
      font-style: italic;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      color: #777;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <%- include("__header.ejs") %>

  <div class="about-container">
    <h1>About Us</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">Delivering meals, connecting hearts.</p>

    <p>
      We are a team of food lovers, tech enthusiasts, and logistics experts working together to simplify food delivery. Whether you're craving something spicy, sweet, or healthy — we aim to get it to your doorstep quickly and reliably.
    </p>

    <h3 class="section-title">Our Purpose</h3>
    <p>
      Life is busy, and meals shouldn't be a hassle. Our goal is to make ordering food as easy as a few taps — giving you back time to enjoy what matters most.
    </p>

    <h3 class="section-title">What We Offer</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Quick access to nearby restaurants and home kitchens</li>
      <li>Live order tracking and reliable delivery times</li>
      <li>Friendly support to assist you at every step</li>
      <li>Secure payments and order history at your fingertips</li>
    </ul>

    <h3 class="section-title">Why It Matters</h3>
    <p>
      Food isn’t just fuel — it’s a part of our culture, our families, our comfort. We believe great meals can brighten days, bring people together, and create lasting memories.
    </p>

    <div class="closing">
      Thank you for choosing us.<br>
      We’re here to serve — one meal at a time.
    </div>
  </div>

  <%- include("__footer.ejs") %>
</body>
</html>
